<h1 class="fw-bold text-center py-4 px-2">Welcome to the Support Forum</h1>
<p class="text-center px-2">Feel free to browse through the list of support threads created by others.</p>
<p class="text-center px-2">You may want to look through the list of support threads created by others before deciding to create one.</p>
<p class="text-center fst-italic pb-4 px-2">A random support thread in the list below may contain the answer you need, thus saving you time!</p>
<hr>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-4 mb-3">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <p class="fw-bold m-0">Create a Thread</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p>Our staff aims to reply to your queries within 48 hours. We thank you for your patience.</p>
                <div class="accordion" id="guidelinesAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-item mb-3">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseGuidelines" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseGuidelines">Posting Guidelines</button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseGuidelines" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#guidelinesAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <ol type="1">
                                    <li>Thread contents must not contain any form of harassment, bullying, or threats of violence.</li>
                                    <li>Respect the privacy of others. Instigating harassment, for example, by revealing someoneâ€™s personal or confidential information, is not allowed.</li>
                                    <li>You are not required to use your real name to create a thread, but you are not allowed in any way to impersonate an individual or an entity misleadingly or deceptively.</li>
                                    <li>Keep thread contents legal, and avoid posting illegal content or soliciting/facilitating unlawful or prohibited transactions.</li>
                                    <li>Do not attempt to perform any actions that interfere with the operations/use of the forum.</li>
                                    <li>Thread cannot be modified or deleted once posted to discourage any misuse of our support forum.</li>
                                </ol>
                                <small class="fw-bold text-danger">Site administrators of CarOrSell have the legal rights to lodge a report against your actions with real-world authorities should we determine it as a potential threat to people's lives.</small>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{#if user}}
                <form action="/thread-creation" method="get">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info w-100">Create a Thread</button>
                </form>
                {{else}}
                <p>You need to be logged in to create a support thread.</p>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-8">
        {% if count == 0 %}
        <p>There are currently no threads created.</p>
        <p class="fst-italic">Why not start one if you really need our assistance?</p>
        {% elif count == 1 %}
        <h3 class="fw-bold">Browse Thread</h3>
        <p>There is 1 thread available for viewing.</p>
        {% else %}
        <h3 class="fw-bold">Browse Threads</h3>
        <p class="mb-0">There are {{ count }} threads available for viewing.</p>
        <p class="fst-italic">Threads are sorted with the latest at the top, to the earliest at the bottom of the page.</p>
        {% endif %}

        {% for threads in threads_list %}
        <div class="card mb-3">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h5 class="fw-bold my-1">{{ threads.get_thread_title() }}</h5>
                <small class="p-0">Posted by: {{ threads.get_thread_username() }}</small>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body py-2">
                <p class="mb-1 fst-italic">Please selection an option:</p>
                {% if session['logged_in_admin'] %}
                <a href="/view-thread/{{ threads.get_thread_id() }}" class="btn btn-info mb-1">View Thread</a>
                <a href="/update-thread/{{ threads.get_thread_id() }}" class="btn btn-warning mb-1">Update Thread</a>
                <hr class="my-1">
                <small class="fw-bold mb-1">DESTRUCTIVE ACTION:</small>
                <form action="{{ url_for('delete_thread', id=threads.get_thread_id()) }}" method="POST">
                    <!-- Modal Codes (DELETE) -->
                    <div class="modal fade" id="staticBackdropDelete_{{ threads.get_thread_id() }}" data-bs-backdrop="static" data-bs-keyboard="false" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="staticBackdropLabel" aria-hidden="true">
                        <div class="modal-dialog">
                            <div class="modal-content">
                                <div class="modal-header">
                                    <h5 class="fw-bold" id="staticBackdropLabel">Thread Deletion Confirmation</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="modal-body">
                                    <p>Are you sure that you would want to delete this support thread titled "{{ threads.get_thread_title() }}"?</p>
                                    <small class="text-danger fw-bold">
                                        <sup>*</sup>This action is irreversible.
                                    </small>
                                </div>
                                <div class="modal-footer">
                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Cancel</button>
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger mb-1">Delete Thread</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Trigger Discard Changes & Go Back Modal -->
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#staticBackdropDelete_{{ threads.get_thread_id() }}">Delete Thread</button>
                </form>
                {% else %}
                <a href="/view-thread/{{ threads.get_thread_id() }}" class="btn btn-info mb-1">View Thread</a>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}

        <!-- Back to Top Button -->
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-info btn-floating btn-lg" id="btn-back-to-top">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-up"></i>
            <p class="fw-bold p-0 m-0" style="font-size: 14px">TOP</p>
        </button>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Script -->
<script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='scripts/btt.js') }}"></script>
{% endblock %}